column5: The hatch is long over & the Alevin are growing nicely, 5 new school's this year & lots of babysitters to help take care of this years crop.  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MSrqRu_MYh8
Doing an awesome job there! The salmon are in very good hands and have a very bright future for many generations down the road. Feel free to send me some photos for our newsletter.  -Eugene-
Thats very cool Richard.  The last 30 sec or so was great to watch. I was rooting the little ones on. Come on,you can do it. LOL   Thanks for taking the time as always.
Thanks for all the hard work...see ya in a few years fish!
